# Input

```yml
plain key: in-line value
: # Both empty
"quoted key":
- entry

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
 plain key: in-line value
 : # Both empty
 "quoted key":
-  - entry
+- entry
\ No newline at end of file
```

# Output

```yml
plain key: in-line value
: # Both empty
"quoted key":
- entry```
